egative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative\nimport Mathlib.Analysis.MeasureTheory.Group.Normed.Oriented.InnerProduct.Euclidean.L2.Real.Normed.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Basic\nimport Mathlib.Analysis.MeasureTheory.Group.Normed.Oriented.InnerProduct.Euclidean.L2.Real.Normed.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative\nimport Mathlib.Analysis.MeasureTheory.Group.Normed.Oriented.InnerProduct.Euclidean.L2.Real.Normed.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Basic\nimport Mathlib.Analysis.MeasureTheory.Group.Normed.Oriented.InnerProduct.Euclidean.L2.Real.Normed.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative\nimport Mathlib.Analysis.MeasureTheory.Group.Normed.Oriented.InnerProduct.Euclidean.L2.Real.Normed.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Basic\nimport Mathlib.Analysis.MeasureTheory.Group.Normed.Oriented.InnerProduct.Euclidean.L2.Real.Normed.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Negative.Neg