These two maps are inverses of each other:
- $(u \cdot x) \cdot u^{-1} = u \cdot (x \cdot u^{-1}) = u \cdot (x \cdot u^{-1}) = x$ (using associativity)
- $x \cdot u \cdot u^{-1} = x \cdot (u \cdot u^{-1}) = x \cdot 1 = x$ (using associativity)

